@startuml tool_call_turn
' Diagram 2/5 — the tool-call turn: manifest shaping, validation, dispatch,
' rendering, loop decisions. Constraints carry their finding numbers.
' Source of truth: src/agora/fleet/{agent_runtime,inner_tools,llm_adapter}.py
' Render: scripts/render_diagrams.py (PlantUML server, docker: plantuml-server)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

participant "AgentRuntime\n_run_loop" as RT
participant "Manifest\nshaping" as MAN
participant "LLM adapter\n(v7 rendering)" as AD
participant "Ollama\ndaemon" as OL
participant "validate_call\n+ dispatch" as VD
participant "Tool\n(inner_tools)" as TOOL
participant "Provenance\nrun.log / tasks.jsonl" as PROV

RT -> MAN : build tool manifest for seat
note right of MAN
  allowlist filter (AgentConfig.allowed_tools)
  **F12**: tool surface is casting evidence
  overwrite guard hides write_file on
  non-empty output — **unless** post-hide
  manifest has zero mutation tools (**F13**)
  every delta logged (**manifest-delta rule**)
end note
MAN -> PROV : manifest deltas (INFO)

RT -> AD : messages + system + tools
AD -> OL : /api/chat
note right of AD
  tool results delivered verbatim,
  one message per result, no markers,
  no re-encoding (**v5–v7**: byte-transparent
  observation channel; models copy
  exactly what they are shown)
end note
OL --> AD : response (tool_calls | content | thinking)
AD --> RT : LLMResponse (thinking surfaced, **S7**)

alt turn has tool calls
  RT -> VD : validate_call(call, schema)
  note right of VD
    **S1** corrective errors: schema echo
    + hint; raw tracebacks never reach
    the model. Role scope enforced here
    and at load-time lint (**F1/F2**)
  end note
  VD -> TOOL : dispatch (validated)
  TOOL --> VD : result string (errors propagate — **F17**)
  VD -> PROV : tool call + result (**F3**: observer always on)
  VD --> RT : rendered result (next turn)
else turn is empty / reasoning-only
  note right of RT
    empty turn + postconditions unmet
    + nudge budget → **S2** nudge (stalls only)
    reasoning-only + salvage budget →
    **S7** re-prompt with own draft
    (scoped: termination-decided turns
    are immune — **F18‴**)
  end note
end

RT -> PROV : TaskRecord (nudges, salvages,\nreviews, run_check captures **F11**)
@enduml
